teradataQuery:
SELECT
SUBSTR('#V_MISDATE#',1,6) AS	REPORTING_PERIOD,
TRIM(CAST(A.ACCT_NBR AS VARCHAR(20))) AS ACCOUNT_NUMBER,
TRIM(UPPER(NVL(cast(CAST(B.ACCT_BOOK_DT   as DATE  format 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9)),'')))  AS   ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE ,
TRIM(B.BR_CDE)  AS BOOK_OF_BUSINESS ,
BOOK_OF_BUSINESS  AS ORIGINATING_BRANCH,
TRIM(UPPER(NVL(cast(CAST(LST_INT_RVSL_DT  AS DATE  format 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9)),'')))  AS DATE_OF_LAST_INTEREST_REVERSAL ,
CAST(CAST(NVL(ALS.N_RT_TERM_INCR,0) AS DECIMAL(38,2)) AS VARCHAR(50)) AS ORIGINAL_AMORTIZATION_PERIOD,
ORIGINAL_AMORTIZATION_PERIOD AS REPAYMENT_TERM ,
TRIM(CASE WHEN  DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT='0' THEN UPPER(NVL(cast(CAST(DLQ.LAST_PYMT_DT  AS DATE  format 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9)),'')) 
			ELSE UPPER(NVL(cast(CAST(PDLQ.LAST_PYMT_DT  AS DATE  format 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9)),'')) END ) AS LAST_FULL_PAYMENT_DATE ,
TRIM(UPPER(NVL(cast(CAST(PDLQ.LOAN_NXT_DUE_DT   as DATE  format 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9)),'')))  AS   LAST_PAYMENT_DUE_DATE ,
LAST_PAYMENT_DUE_DATE   AS   FIRST_PAYMENT_DATE ,
TRIM(UPPER(NVL(cast(CAST(DLQ.LOAN_NXT_DUE_DT  as DATE  format 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9)),'')))  AS   NEXT_PAYMENT_DUE_DATE,
TRIM(CAST(CAST(A.REMAINING_TNR  AS DECIMAL(38,2)) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS REMAINING_TERM,
CASE  
			 WHEN A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'CL' AND B.ACCT_STAT_RSN_CDE = 'PT'  THEN '0' WHEN A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'CL' AND B.ACCT_STAT_RSN_CDE NOT IN ( 'PT') THEN '1'
			 WHEN B.PRCS_STAT_CDE = 'CF' THEN '0'  ELSE (CASE WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT = 0 THEN '1' ELSE '0' END ) END AS PAID_IN_FULL_CODING  ,
			 
CASE  WHEN NVL(B.PRCS_STAT_CDE,'') ='CF' THEN '9' WHEN  NVL(A.ACCT_STAT_CDE,'')='CL'  THEN  '3'   Else  '0'    END  AS   ACCOUNT_STATUS_CLOSED_MOED ,			 

ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE  AS   LOAN_FUNDING_CLOSE_DATE,
UPPER(nvl(cast(CAST(B.ACCT_ORIG_MAT_DT  as DATE  format 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9)),''))  AS  ORIGINAL_LOAN_MATURITY_DATE,
Case When ORIG_AMT=0 Then 0 Else (A.ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT/ORIG_AMT) End   AS ORIGINAL_LOAN_TO_VALUE ,  
TRIM (CAST((A.MIS_DT-B.ACCT_BOOK_DT MONTH(4)) AS VARCHAR(5)) ) AS  MONTHS_ON_BOOK_LOCAL,

ORIGINAL_AMORTIZATION_PERIOD  AS ORIGINAL_LOAN_TERM ,
TRIM(NVL(CAST( CASE WHEN ALS.N_RT_TERM_INCR <= 120 then '14'
WHEN ALS.N_RT_TERM_INCR <= 180 then '3'
WHEN ALS.N_RT_TERM_INCR <= 240 then '2'
WHEN ALS.N_RT_TERM_INCR <= 360 then '1' else '13' END  AS CHAR(2) ),'')) AS MORTGAGE_TYPE_2 ,
CASE WHEN OLD_ACCT_NBR IS NOT NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END as TOP_UP_FLAG ,
CASE WHEN BIL.BILL_SKIP_MTHS_CNT > 0 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N'  END AS  SKIP_A_PAYMENT ,
CASE WHEN ALS.V_RT_ACCT_TYPE ='300' THEN  'RE_FR' ELSE  'CO_SI'  END AS PRODUCT_CCAR_TYPE ,
TRIM(CASE  WHEN  (A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'CL' AND B.ACCT_STAT_RSN_CDE = 'PT') THEN  UPPER(NVL(cast(CAST( A.ACCT_STAT_CHG_DT AS DATE  format 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9)),''))  ELSE '' End)  As  ACTUAL_PAYOFF_DATE,
'Y' NON_TRADITIONAL_MORTGAGE , 
CASE WHEN A.GL_STAT_CDE= '1000'  THEN '0'  ELSE '1' END  AS  ACCRUAL_STATUS ,
MORTGAGE_TYPE_2  AS MORTGAGE_TYPE_AT_ORIGIN ,
ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE    AS  LAST_FUNDS_ADVANCED_DATE ,
UPPER(nvl(cast(CAST(B.ACCT_CURR_MAT_DT  as DATE  format 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9)),''))   AS  CURR_LOAN_LEASE_MATURITY_DATE,
ORIGINAL_LOAN_MATURITY_DATE AS  LOAN_TERM_END_DATE ,
TRIM(CAST( CAST( A.ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT  AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS LOAN_AMOUNT ,
(Case When (Cast(Cast(B.ACCT_BOOK_DT As date format 'YYYYMM') As Char(6)) = Cast(Cast(A.MIS_DT As date format 'YYYYMM') As Char(6))) Then Coalesce(A.ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT,0) Else 0 end)  AS LOAN_ADVANCES  ,
(CASE WHEN RVL.ACCT_COFF_DT Is Not NULL OR  (A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'CL' AND  A.ACCT_STAT_CHG_DT IS NOT Null )
THEN 0 ELSE
                                                                                CASE WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT =0 THEN 0 
                                                                                WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 30 THEN 1
                                                                                WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 60 THEN 2
                                                                                WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 90 THEN 3
                                                                                WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 120 THEN 4
                                                                                WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 150 THEN 5
                                                                                WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 180 THEN 6
                                                                                ELSE 7 END END)   AS  PAYMENT_MISSED_COUNT ,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
TRIM(CAST( CAST( (A.TOT_MTD_PAID_ACYAMT + A.FEE_PAID_OFF_THIS_MTH_ACYAMT + A.INT_PAID_OFF_THIS_MTH_ACYAMT)  AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS PAYMENT_AMOUNT_MONTH_END ,
TRIM(CAST( CAST( A.PRIN_PAID_OFF_THIS_MTH_ACYAMT  AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS PRINCIPAL_PAID,

Case When A_SUM.ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT_SUM Is Not Null Or A_SUM.ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT_SUM = 0  Then ((A.ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT * CL.N_COLL_FMV)/ A_SUM.ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT_SUM) Else (A.ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT * CL.N_COLL_FMV) End As ORIG_AMT,
Case When ORIG_AMT=0 Then 0 Else (A.ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT/ORIG_AMT) End As ORIGINAL_COMBINED_LTV ,


TRIM(CAST( CAST( A.LOAN_UNPAID_INSTMT_ACYAMT  AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS MINIMUM_PAYMENT_DUE ,

TRIM(CAST( CAST( A.ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT  AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS TOTAL_FUNDS_DISBURSED  ,
CASE WHEN RVL.ACCT_COFF_DT IS NOT NULL  THEN  0  ELSE (A.TOT_ASSS_FEE_ACYAMT + A.TOT_LATE_FEE_ASSS_ACYAMT)  END AS OUTSTANDING_FEES  ,
(CASE WHEN  DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT >= 90 THEN 0 ELSE  Coalesce(A.LOAN_INT_ACCR_NOT_PAID_ACYAMT,0) end ) + (Case WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT >= 90 then 0 else Coalesce(a.TOT_LATE_FEE_ASSS_ACYAMT,0)+Coalesce(a.TOT_ASSS_FEE_ACYAMT,0) end ) AS ACCRUED_INTEREST_AND_FEE,
((case when RVL.ACCT_COFF_DT is null then A.TOT_ASSS_FEE_ACYAMT+A.TOT_LATE_FEE_ASSS_ACYAMT else 0 end) +(case when B.PRCS_STAT_CDE='CF' then 0 else A.TOT_INT_DUE_ACYAMT end))  AS  OUTSTANDING_INTEREST_AND_FEE,
TRIM(CAST( CAST( A.FEE_PAID_OFF_THIS_MTH_ACYAMT  AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50)))  as FEE_PAYMENTS ,
TRIM(CAST( CAST( CASE WHEN NVL(A.INT_PAID_OFF_THIS_MTH_ACYAMT,0)=0 THEN '0.00' ELSE CAST(CAST(A.INT_PAID_OFF_THIS_MTH_ACYAMT AS DECIMAL(20,5)) AS VARCHAR(30)) END   AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) 
AS VARCHAR(50))) AS INTEREST_PAYMENTS ,
TRIM(CAST( CAST( case when B.PRCS_STAT_CDE = 'Y' then 0 else A.TOT_INT_DUE_ACYAMT end  AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS OUTSTANDING_INTEREST ,
TRIM(CAST( CAST( (CASE WHEN  DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT >= 90 THEN 0 ELSE  Coalesce(A.LOAN_INT_ACCR_NOT_PAID_ACYAMT,0) end )  AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS ACCRUED_INTEREST_AMOUNT ,
TRIM(CAST( CAST( (Case WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT >= 90 then 0 else Coalesce(A.TOT_LATE_FEE_ASSS_ACYAMT,0)+Coalesce(A.TOT_ASSS_FEE_ACYAMT,0) end )   AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS ACCRUED_FEES_AMOUNT ,
CR.EXPNS_LCY   AS EXPENSES ,


B.PRD_CDE  AS LOCAL_PRODUCT_ID,
TRIM(CAST( Case When A.PRD_CDE In ('0801','0802','0810') And ALS.V_RT_ACCT_TYPE='300' Then (Case When ALS.N_RT_TERM_INCR >180 Then '1Mort_VFTL' Else '1Mort_VFTS' End) 
Else 'OthSecInst' End  AS VARCHAR(20) )) AS BASEL_PRODUCT,
TRIM(CAST(  DLQ.BUCKET_CDE  AS VARCHAR(3) )) AS LOCAL_DELQ_BUCKET_MONTH_END ,
TRIM(CAST( DLQ.LOAN_DELQ_HISTORY_STR  AS VARCHAR(40) )) AS DELQ_STRING_24_MTH_MONTH_END ,
TRIM(CAST( CASE WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT >  0 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N'   END AS VARCHAR(1) )) AS DELINQUENCY_FLAG ,
TRIM(CAST(CAST( DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT   AS DECIMAL(38,2)) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS DAYS_PAST_DUE_MONTH_END ,
TRIM (UPPER(CAST( CAST( RVL.ACCT_COFF_DT  AS DATE FORMAT 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9) ))) AS FULL_CHARGE_OFF_DATE ,
TRIM(CAST( CASE WHEN B.PRCS_STAT_CDE='CF' THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END   AS VARCHAR(1) )) AS CHARGE_OFF_FLAG ,
A.INSTMT_ACYAMT AS ORIGINAL_MONTHLY_PAYMENT,
TRIM(CAST( CAST( CASE WHEN NVL(B.LOAN_ORIG_INT_RTE,0)=0 THEN '0.00' ELSE CAST(CAST(B.LOAN_ORIG_INT_RTE AS DECIMAL(7,5)) AS VARCHAR(20)) END   AS DECIMAL(7,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS ORIGINAL_INTEREST_RATE ,
CASE WHEN  B.PRD_CDE IN ('0801','0802','0810') THEN (CASE WHEN B.ACCT_TYP_CDE = '100' THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END) ELSE  'N' END AS  PROMO_INTEREST_RATE_ELIGIBLE, 
TRIM(CAST( CAST( A.LOAN_CURR_INT_RTE  AS DECIMAL(7,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS INTEREST_RATE_MONTH_END ,
TRIM(CAST(TOPUP.OLD_ACCT_NBR AS VARCHAR(20)))  as ORIGINAL_ACCOUNT_NUMBER_1 , 
TRIM(UPPER(CAST( CAST( CASE WHEN (TOP_UP_FLAG='Y' ) THEN TOPUP.ACCT_BOOK_DT ELSE B.ACCT_BOOK_DT END   AS DATE FORMAT 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9) ))) AS FIRST_APPROVAL_DATE,
FIRST_APPROVAL_DATE  AS LAST_APPROVAL_DATE ,
DECODE(TRIM(CAST( CLI.CLNT_STAFF_IND  AS VARCHAR(1) )),'Y','Y','N') AS CITIGROUP_STAFF_ACCT_IND ,
TRIM(CAST(CAST( DLQ.LOAN_PYMT_GRACE_DAYS_CNT   AS DECIMAL(38,2)) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS GRACE_PERIOD_DAY_COUNT,
TRIM(UPPER(CAST( CAST( RT.RTE_ADJ_END_DT  AS DATE FORMAT 'DDMMMYYYY') AS CHAR(9) ))) AS ARM_LAST_RESET_DATE ,
CASE WHEN A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'CL' AND B.ACCT_STAT_RSN_CDE = 'PT'  THEN '9'  WHEN A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'CL' AND B.ACCT_STAT_RSN_CDE NOT IN ( 'PT') THEN '8' WHEN B.PRCS_STAT_CDE = 'CF' THEN '11'
ELSE (CASE WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT = 0 THEN '3' ELSE '4' END ) END AS ACCOUNT_STATUS ,
TRIM(CAST( CAST( Case when RVL.ACCT_COFF_DT <= A.MIS_DT then 0 when A.TOT_PRIN_BAL_ACYAMT > 0 then A.TOT_PRIN_BAL_ACYAMT else 0 end  AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS NET_OUTSTNG_PRIN_BAL_MOED  ,
TRIM(CAST(A.CLNT_NBR AS VARCHAR(20))) AS UNIQUE_CUSTOMER_ID,
TRIM(CAST( CAST( CASE WHEN RT.RTE_ADJ_END_DT IS NULL OR RT.RTE_ADJ_END_DT = '9999-12-31' OR 
B.ACCT_BOOK_DT  IS NULL THEN '0' ELSE  cast(cast(((RT.RTE_ADJ_END_DT - B.ACCT_BOOK_DT ) month(4)) as integer) as varchar(5)) END  AS INTEGER ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS ARM_INITIAL_RATE_PERIOD,
TRIM(UPPER(CAST( CAST( CASE WHEN NVL(CL.V_UDF_131,'00000000') = '00000000' OR CAST(NVL(CL.V_UDF_131,'16000101') AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMMDD') > B.ACCT_BOOK_DT THEN B.ACCT_BOOK_DT ELSE CAST(CL.V_UDF_131 AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMMDD') END AS DATE FORMAT 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9) ))) AS ORIGINAL_COLL_VALUATION_DATE ,
TRIM(UPPER(CAST( CAST( DLQ.LAST_PYMT_DT  AS DATE FORMAT 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9) ))) AS LAST_PAYMENT_DATE ,
Case When NVL(B.PRCS_STAT_CDE,'') ='CF' Then ''  When A.ACCT_STAT_CDE='CL' Then '' Else 'EFF' End As  ACCT_SUSPENSION_TEMP_BLOCK_RSN ,
TRIM(CAST( CAST( A.ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT  AS DECIMAL(20,5) ) AS VARCHAR(50))) AS ORIGINAL_PRINCIPAL_AMOUNT  ,
CASE  WHEN A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'OPEN'    THEN  ACCOUNT_OPEN_DATE WHEN A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'CLOSED'  THEN  TRIM(UPPER(CAST( CAST( B.ACCT_CLSE_DT  AS DATE FORMAT 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9) ))) END  AS ACCT_SUSPENSION_TEMP_BLOCK_DT ,
TRIM(DLQ.EVER_90_DPD_L12M_IND) AS EVER_90_DPD_PAST_12_MONTHS  ,
CASE WHEN A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'CL' THEN UPPER(cast(CAST( A.ACCT_STAT_CHG_DT AS DATE  format 'DDMMMYYYY') AS VARCHAR(9))) ELSE CAST(CAST(NULL AS DATE ) AS VARCHAR(20)) End  As  CLOSED_DATE ,

(CASE WHEN RVL.ACCT_COFF_DT Is Not NULL OR  (Case When A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'CL' Then  A.ACCT_STAT_CHG_DT Else Null End) Is Not NULL 
THEN 'X' ELSE
					CASE 
					WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT =0    THEN '0' 
					WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 30  THEN '1'
					WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 60  THEN '2'
					WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 90  THEN '3'
					WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 120 THEN '4'
					WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 150 THEN '5'
					WHEN DLQ.TOT_DPD_CNT < 180 THEN '6'
					ELSE '7' END
END) AS DELQ_BAND_NORMALIZED_MONTH_END ,
(CASE WHEN RVL.ACCT_COFF_DT <=  A.MIS_DT THEN 0 Else A.TOT_PRIN_BAL_ACYAMT END) AS GROSS_OUTSTNG_PRIN_BAL_MOED,
A.INSTMT_ACYAMT AS PRIN_AND_INT_AMT_AT_ORIGIN,
A.INSTMT_ACYAMT AS CURR_PRINCIPAL_AND_INT_AMOUNT,
'1357906910' AS GLOBAL_ORGANIZATION_CODE,
'4587' AS MANAGED_SEGMENT_ID


FROM P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_AST_MASTER B
INNER JOIN P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_AST_SNAPSHOT_M A          
                ON          (A.ACCT_NBR = B.ACCT_NBR             AND       A.PRD_CDE = B.PRD_CDE   AND                A.MIS_DT=CAST(CAST(B.reporting_period  AS VARCHAR(10)) AS DATE format 'YYYYMMDD')) 
INNER JOIN 
                    (SELECT ACCT_NBR, PRD_CDE  , MIS_DT , ACCT_STAT_CDE ,ACCT_COLAT_REF_NBR,
Sum(ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT) Over (Partition by ACCT_COLAT_REF_NBR,ACCT_STAT_CDE) As ORIG_LOAN_ACYAMT_SUM
FROM P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_AST_SNAPSHOT_M
WHERE MIS_DT = CAST('#V_MISDATE#' AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMMDD')
AND PRD_CDE IN ('0801','0802','0810')
) A_SUM
ON 
       (A_SUM.ACCT_NBR = A.ACCT_NBR             AND       A_SUM.PRD_CDE = A.PRD_CDE   AND                A_SUM.MIS_DT=A.MIS_DT)

LEFT OUTER JOIN P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_CLIENT_MASTER CLI ON B.CLNT_NBR = CLI.CLNT_NBR and B.reporting_period = CLI.reporting_period
LEFT OUTER JOIN P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_ACCT_MASTER ACM
                ON          (ACM.ACCT_NBR = B.ACCT_NBR       AND       ACM.PRD_CDE = B.PRD_CDE             AND                ACM.REPORTING_PERIOD=B.REPORTING_PERIOD) 
LEFT OUTER JOIN P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_AST_DELQ_SNAPSHOT_M DLQ
                ON          (A.ACCT_NBR = DLQ.ACCT_NBR       AND       A.PRD_CDE = DLQ.PRD_CDE             AND       A.MIS_DT=DLQ.MIS_DT) 
LEFT OUTER JOIN P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_AST_DELQ_SNAPSHOT_M PDLQ
                ON          (A.ACCT_NBR = PDLQ.ACCT_NBR     AND       A.PRD_CDE = PDLQ.PRD_CDE           AND       (A.MIS_DT - EXTRACT(DAY FROM A.MIS_DT))=PDLQ.MIS_DT) 
LEFT OUTER JOIN P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_AST_REVLOSS_SNAPSHOT_M RVL
                ON          (A.ACCT_NBR = RVL.ACCT_NBR        AND       A.PRD_CDE = RVL.PRD_CDE              AND       A.MIS_DT=RVL.MIS_DT) 
LEFT OUTER JOIN P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_AST_REVLOSS_SNAPSHOT_M PRVL
                ON          (A.ACCT_NBR = PRVL.ACCT_NBR        AND       A.PRD_CDE = PRVL.PRD_CDE              AND       (A.MIS_DT - EXTRACT(DAY FROM A.MIS_DT))=PRVL.MIS_DT) 
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SEL ACCT_NBR,PRD_CDE,MIS_DT,RTE_ADJ_END_DT FROM P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_AST_RATE_ADJ_SNAPSHOT_M 
                                                                QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY ACCT_NBR,PRD_CDE,MIS_DT ORDER BY RTE_ADJ_END_DT DESC) =1) RT
                ON A.ACCT_NBR=RT.ACCT_NBR AND A.PRD_CDE=RT.PRD_CDE AND A.MIS_DT=RT.MIS_DT
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT V_RT_ACCT_NUM ACCT_NBR,SUBSTR(V_CF_CUST_NUM,6) CLNT_NBR,V_RT_ACCT_TYPE,MIS_DATE,N_RT_TERM_INCR,substr(MOEND,1,6) MTH,
max(mis_date) over (partition by v_rt_acct_num)  as MAX_MIS_DATE ,
                                                                CAST(CAST(MIS_DATE AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMMDD') AS VARCHAR(8)) MOEND  FROM P_ID_HDBRISK_V.S_ID_ALS_AMBIR1N_M WHERE MTH = SUBSTR('#V_MISDATE#',1,6) 
                                                                QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY ACCT_NBR,MTH ORDER BY MIS_DATE DESC)=1) ALS
                ON B.ACCT_NBR=ALS.ACCT_NBR AND ALS.MAX_MIS_DATE=ALS.MIS_DATE
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT V_ACCT_NO AS ACCT_NBR, V_CUST_NO AS CLNT_NBR , V_UDF_131,CAST(CAST(MIS_DATE AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMMDD') AS VARCHAR(8)) MOEND,substr(MOEND,1,6) MTH,
                                                      N_COLL_FMV ,           V_COLL_CODE FROM P_ID_HDBRISK_V.S_ALL_CLTRL_MASTER WHERE MTH = SUBSTR('#V_MISDATE#',1,6)         QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY ACCT_NBR,MTH ORDER BY MIS_DATE DESC)=1) CL
                ON A.ACCT_COLAT_REF_NBR=CL.V_COLL_CODE AND CAST(CAST(A.MIS_DT AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMM') AS VARCHAR(6))=CL.MTH
LEFT OUTER JOIN (Select ACCT_NBR,PRD_CDE,ACCT_SOLD_DT,PRD_ID,SOLD_AMT,APPL_NBR,RPTNG_MTH_END_DT , EXPNS_LCY  FROM P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_CREDIT_RISK_SNAPSHOT_M 
                                                                QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER () OVER (PARTITION BY ACCT_NBR,PRD_CDE,RPTNG_MTH_END_DT ORDER BY ACCT_SOLD_DT DESC)=1 ) CR
                ON A.ACCT_NBR = CR.ACCT_NBR AND A.PRD_CDE = CR.PRD_CDE AND A.MIS_DT = CR.RPTNG_MTH_END_DT
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT ACCT_NBR,PRD_CDE,BILL_PYMT_MTHD_CDE,BILL_STRT_DT,BILL_FLAT_AMT ,MIS_DT ,BILL_SKIP_MTHS_CNT FROM P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_AST_BILL_SCH_SNAPSHOT_M
                                                QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER () OVER (PARTITION BY ACCT_NBR,PRD_CDE,MIS_DT ORDER BY BILL_STRT_DT DESC)=1 ) BIL
                ON A.ACCT_NBR = BIL.ACCT_NBR AND A.PRD_CDE = BIL.PRD_CDE AND A.MIS_DT = BIL.MIS_DT
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT MAX(CASE WHEN TXN_ID IN ('9011', '8010') THEN TXN_DT END) AS LST_FEE_RVSL_DT,MAX(CASE WHEN TXN_ID = '9357' THEN TXN_DT END) AS LST_INT_RVSL_DT ,
                                                ACCT_NBR, PRD_CDE, MIS_DT FROM P_ID_HDBRISK_T.INT_AST_TXN_SNAPSHOT_M   GROUP BY ACCT_NBR, PRD_CDE, MIS_DT) TXN
                ON A.ACCT_NBR = TXN.ACCT_NBR AND A.PRD_CDE = TXN.PRD_CDE AND A.MIS_DT = TXN.MIS_DT
LEFT OUTER JOIN (select A.ACCT_NBR AS OLD_ACCT_NBR,A.CLNT_NBR,A.ACCT_STAT_CDE,A.PRD_cDE,A.LOAN_CURR_INT_RTE,B.ACCT_BOOK_DT,B.ACCT_CLSE_DT,A.MIS_DT,
                                MAX(B.ACCT_BOOK_DT) OVER (PARTITION BY A.CLNT_NBR,B.ACCT_CLSE_DT,A.LOAN_CURR_INT_RTE) MAX_ORIG_BOOK_DT,COUNT(A.ACCT_NBR) OVER (PARTITION BY A.CLNT_NBR)  AS CNT
 FROM P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_AST_SNAPSHOT_M A 
LEFT OUTER JOIN           (SELECT ACCT_NBR,ACCT_BOOK_DT,PRD_CDE,ACCT_CLSE_DT,PRD_KEY,CAST(CAST(REPORTING_PERIOD AS VARCHAR(8)) AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMMDD') REP_PRD,
  REPORTING_PERIOD   FROM  P_ID_HDBRISK_V.INT_AST_MASTER WHERE MIS_DT>CAST('20131025' as DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMMDD')  ) b
                ON A.ACCT_NBR=B.ACCT_NBR AND A.PRD_CDE=B.PRD_CDE AND A.MIS_DT=B.REP_PRD WHERE 
                B.REPORTING_PERIOD= #V_MISDATE# AND 
                A.PRD_CDE IN ('0801','0802','0810') AND B.PRD_KEY='0' ) TOPUP 
ON a.CLNT_NBR=TOPUP.CLNT_NBR and b.ACCT_BOOK_DT=TOPUP.ACCT_CLSE_DT and a.LOAN_CURR_INT_RTE=TOPUP.LOAN_CURR_INT_RTE AND A.MIS_DT=TOPUP.MIS_DT
WHERE TRIM(B.PRD_CDE) IN ('0801', '0802', '0810')  AND            B.PRD_KEY = '0' AND           ( ( A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'AC' or (A.ACCT_STAT_CDE = 'CL' AND         (A.ACCT_STAT_CHG_DT - A.MIS_DT) MONTH(4) = 0) ) ) 
AND (TOPUP.ACCT_BOOK_DT IS NULL OR MAX_ORIG_BOOK_DT=TOPUP.ACCT_BOOK_DT)
AND B.REPORTING_PERIOD= #V_MISDATE#
Qualify row_number() over(partition by A.ACCT_NBR, A.PRD_CDE order by OLD_ACCT_NBR)=1
